Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation Odessa ended in\Nvictory for the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, the Zeon forces\Nwere driven back from Europe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the war was\Nproceeding in a new direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Char Returns
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, Gunperry?\NDocking searcher, 5, 4, 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead with the B Parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Core change! Docking, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You still haven't broken\Nthe 17 second mark in docking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Core Fighter was meant to be\Nan escape capsule for the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quick to get out, but not to get back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be impossible,\Nbut Amuro can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base is headed for a Federation\Nsupply base in Northern Ireland...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...to repair damage incurred in\Nthe battle at Odessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I finally have a chance to cut loose\Nand relax for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- I wouldn't be so sure.\N- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our destination is\Na Federation Forces dock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It means we're officially part of the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what we may be\Nordered to do from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That certainly took the fun out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen that type of warship before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Unknown warship entering Dock 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Type unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir. We've been contacted by No. 107.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better inform the captain about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a report from No. 107...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...that a large warship has entered SR4.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This picture is useless.\NThere's just too much radio interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. I can't make it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Boone's team\Nstationed in this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the Sealance ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as we've checked the surface,\Nbring up the Mad Angler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You could just order\NBoone to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, if it's the Trojan Horse,\NI'd like to see for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Kycilia would laugh,\Nbut I too have my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, sir.\NThe Mad Angler will be waiting right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Mulligan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I came across the Trojan Horse right after\Nmy transfer to the Mad Angler squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a fortunate man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The latest report says the external repairs\Nshould be done by tomorrow, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I do wish I had the luxury\Nof giving the crew a week's rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where are they now?\N- Sir! We've gathered them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey!\N- Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You naughty kids! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute to General Revil!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Neener neener!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job. Please be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All crew, at ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I can thank you all\Nfor your efforts since you left Side 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,After receiving temporary repairs here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll go to Federation headquarters\Nat Jaburo, in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. What about people who aren't\Ninterested in joining the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all very capable soldiers, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you decide to leave the military now,\Nwe'd have to imprison you for at least a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're forcing people who don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have all been exposed to\Nthe military's greatest secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, we'd be required\Nto imprison you for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A soldier, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving on to a more important subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zeon Forces have recently\Nbecome quite active.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Spurred on by the appearance\Nof the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...they're devoting all their resources\Nto the mass production of mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is still unconfirmed intelligence, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the Zeons have learned\Nfrom our use of the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for quantity\Nif the mobile suits are powerful enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:08:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to feel that one or two will be\Nenough to obtain the desired results.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,G-General! Those diagrams on the monitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they all different types of mobile suits?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe so. Furthermore, Zeon is testing\Na new design they call "mobile armor."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile... armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This one Gundam has primed the pump.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Primed the pump?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's attacks will become\Neven fiercer. In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll inform you of any new intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you consider\Nyour countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No. 2! Once you've released your Goggs,\Nmake a detour to enter from the north!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you sink the Trojan Horse\Nbefore Captain Char arrives!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Goggs, ready for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Goggs should reach the Trojan Horse\Nin about eight minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll cover the landing of the Goggs by firing\Nmissiles 30 seconds before they arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Man. What a hassle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Soldier! Won't you buy something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing in there worth buying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all locally made. And, delicious too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty cute!\NThough, it looks like you have a tough life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then buy something.\N- Maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheapskate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, buy something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That old man is very nice, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- You don't wanna join, Fraw Bow?\N- It's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we join the military...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'll take care of the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all used to the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- You have a point there.\N- Come on, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe for you\Nhere on the dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Go play over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta clean all the White Base's toilets\Nand change the bed covers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:10:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- We got tons of things to do!\N- Ungrateful brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be cruel to separate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Marshy! We're on schedule to reach\Nthe harbor housing the Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Right!this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're awfully small. Could they be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Just as I feared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hats off to the Gogg. Not even a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Releasing Freeze Gel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost response from Area 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go to alert status.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Our approach looks problem-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Boone!\NI'm counting on your attack to cover us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time... Fire missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Missiles detected!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- From Area 22?!\N- No, from 54!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- What should we do?!\N- Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of the mobile suits\Nare ready to sortie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Only the Gundam, sir.cannon?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guncannon's getting an overhaul.es.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro says he'll launch in the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard he can't use the beam rifle.\NPlease check with the mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, you may proceed.\NJust don't damage the dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, come on. Fraw Bow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're beginning to talk like Ms. Sayla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Really? I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. It's all going according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Lasa! Marshy here.\NI'm on shore, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like mobile suits have landed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them near the dock!\NProtect the White Base no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you seriously think those vulcans\Nwill penetrate Gogg's armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that also a new type of mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks different from the Zakus or Goufs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, if that thing came from the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...it might be the Gogg type,\Nwhich was developed to be amphibious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,General. It's unsafe out here. The shelter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No. If it's our time to die,\Nit makes no difference where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If the commander of an army is content\Nto shout orders from the rear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...he'll lose even a winning battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be true, sir, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we defend against\Nattacks from the right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! I'll pass that on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening with our defense line\Nfrom Areas 60 to 65?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sir! We've just requested\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, everything always\Ncomes down to mobile suits...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how times have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is right in front of us!\NMove G-Bull to Hatch 3 and send it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying I shouldn't be\Nin the G-Bull when we send it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly. But if you stay here for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...we can use the Gundam\Nand G-Fighter later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A difficult choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Our tactics rely too much\Non the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then. I'll take off in the G-Fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't yet. The main engine still needs\Na bit more work done on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!\NHurry up, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway... move the G-Fighter to Deck 3\Nso that it's ready for takeoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow. Tell Hayato to hurry\Nand head out in the Guntank!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!\NHayato! Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guntank, moving out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guntank, heading out! Open the gate for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are those missiles coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,White Base! Please provide some info!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That town...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The vulcan guns don't seem to affect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But... at that speed...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you, you Gun... thingamajig!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gogg won't lose to your horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This hammer's been powered up, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What in the world are you doing\Nstill wandering around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry. Bye, Mr. Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're not soldiers either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Mr. Kai. You'd better hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Amuro! Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had the beam rifle,\NI'd take out this mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second... Fraw Bow!\NCan the G-Parts be used yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's see. Yes, they can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Have them get the G-Bull parts ready!\N- Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? He retreated?! That Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit that scares even the Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Omur! Please have the Gundam's\NB Parts ready to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know what'll happen in a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ms. Sayla!\NWe're taking off! Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one unusually large tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This cockpit is so strong,\Nit can withstand a direct beam blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,M... Marshy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro. The other mobile suit\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:18:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you check with White Base?\NFind out if the B Parts are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you don't need to\Nreturn to the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Omur and the others are preparing\Nfor a mid-air transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pilot it this time, okay Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Okay, continue...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Slower!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's wrong with the elevator?\N- The pressure pipe hasn't been fixed yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparations to send out\NG-Armor's B Parts are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up Central Hatch 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're launching the G-Armor's B Parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When the mobile suit vanished,\Nthe missile bombardment stopped as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! The enemy mobile suits emerged\Nfrom the ocean, didn't they? Fraw Bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please inform Sayla that she must\Ncover the Gundam with the G-Fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Docking searcher synchronized! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Control system is switched over!\NGundam, separating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! You need to take extra care\Nwhen pursuing the enemy, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's the Gundam!\NIt's dangerous to pursue too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh... Where Is he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell for it, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One more shot from the beam cannons,\Nand you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The monitor! I can't use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The monitor's gone out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... Who won?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the battle's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Amuro! Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam! Gundam! Please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear the radio?\NAmuro! Please... respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the Gundam won.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If the enemy had won,\Nthey'd be attacking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course... it's also possible\Nthat they destroyed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see something moving underwater!\NI'll send you an image of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm receiving an image from the G-Fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Connection...restored...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you hear me, White Base... ?\NI'm returning to ship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright! Amuro's on his way back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's great.\N- He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Captain Char!\NStandby to take in his Sealance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's the Captain for you!\NHis skill is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, all right. The Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But... both Goggs that sent us\Nthis video have been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.86,0:22:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's only to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.86,0:22:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That mobile suit isn't a\Ncheap mass-produced type.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... I am ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite all right, Boone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't rest until I bring this guy down...\Nwith my own two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know it's childish...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:23:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is the mobile suit\Nthat injured my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Under Char's command...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...fierce attacks on the White Base continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai Shiden's distaste for the military\Nleads him to say good-bye to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.43,0:23:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...but later, he rejoins the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However... close behind him\Nis a young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.11,0:23:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NA Spy on Board.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A Spy on Board
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.55,0:23:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
